# Allowlist model: ignore EVERYTHING, then re-include only what the
# published extension needs. Any new file is excluded by default.
#
# The production build (npm run build / tsconfig.build.json) emits ONLY
# runtime code to dist/ — tests (src/test) are excluded and source maps
# are off — so shipping "!dist/**" is safe and needs no maintenance when
# new source files or folders are added.
**/*

!package.json
!README.md
!CHANGELOG.md
!LICENCE
!assets/**
!dist/**
